3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper studies the dynamics of the system using queueing models. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper may involve multimedia traffic in the cellular networks. 
5. cs.PF (Performance) is another less likely category but still possible as the paper evaluates the performance of different combinations of UA and RA schemes.
